title: Marquette Madness slam dunk contest highlights
text:
Marquette Madness slam dunk contest highlights FOX Sports 
Oct 10, 2015 at 2:47p ET + 
Henry Ellenson won the slam dunk contest title on Friday night. Maggie Bean Updated Oct 10, 2015 at 2:47p ET 
Marquette Madness included a competitive dunk contest on Friday night at the Al McGuire Center. 
Henry Ellenson, the 6-foot-10 freshman, won the slam dunk title, defeating Sandy Cohen, Sacar Anim and Wally Ellenson, his older brother.
